## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| Near-duplicate | Code with same logic but minor syntactic differences |
| Dead Code | Code that is unreachable from any entry point |
| Confidence Score | Probability estimate that code is truly dead |
| Git Mining | Semantic search over git commit history |
| Reachability | Whether a function can be reached from entry points via call graph |
| Embedding Similarity | Cosine distance between vector representations of code |

